org.logicmill.util.concurrent

Class ConcurrentHashMapInspector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logicmill.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMapInspector

  • public class ConcurrentHashMapInspector
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility associated with ConcurrentHashMap that collects and reports performance-related statistics about a map's internal structure, focusing particularly on bucket structure. To apply this class to a map instance, construct an inspector object with a reference to the map instance: 
    
 ConcurrentHashMap<Key,Value> map = new ConcurrentHashMap<Key,Value>(1024, 8, 0.8F);
 ConcurrentHashMapInspector inspector = new ConcurrentHashMapInspector(map);
 ...

    David Curtis
